Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model

Class Model

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.ModelObservable
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.ModelObservableWithSelect
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Model
public class Model
extends ModelObservableWithSelect
Model class that specifies the single match, containing the list of players, the gameMap, the Set of chosen Cards and Colors and the jsonPath. PossibleDst Arrays contains the list of Cells in which the player can move or build
